{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01VX2CD1oyv4ToWmRbAGynSv","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-25\n     2→\n     3→### 15-4-fix-ts-compilation-errors — create-story (2026-03-25T05:55Z)\n     4→\n     5→**Problems encountered:**\n     6→- Original story quoted ~40 errors; actual count is 106. Epic definition was stale.\n     7→\n     8→**Risks identified:**\n     9→- AC2 (\"type annotation changes only\") boundary between type-only and logic change can be blurry\n    10→- 4 source files (not just test files) have errors, carrying higher risk\n    11→- 106 errors is large scope for single story\n    12→\n    13→**Observations:**\n    14→- All 5 ACs are cli-verifiable — fully automatable\n    15→- Error count has been growing for 13+ sessions\n    16→\n    17→### 15-4-fix-ts-compilation-errors — dev-story (2026-03-25T06:13Z)\n    18→\n    19→**Problems encountered:**\n    20→- None — all 106 errors fixed across 20 files.\n    21→\n    22→**Borderline logic changes:**\n    23→- `dimensions.ts`: Changed `g.message` → `g.description`, removed nonexistent `g.fix`. Prior code was broken at runtime (undefined properties).\n    24→- `run.ts`: Changed `'in-review'` → `'review'` to match StoryStatus type. Other system parts (bash/yaml) may still use `'in-review'`.\n    25→- `docker-setup.ts`: `opensearch` property not in HarnessState interface but code writes it. Used `as HarnessState` cast.\n    26→\n    27→**Workarounds applied:**\n    28→- `deps.test.ts`/`otlp.test.ts`: Explicit parameter typing for overloaded mock callbacks (vitest limitation with overloaded functions).\n    29→- `scan-cache.test.ts`: Removed `hasBmalph`/`bmalpthFiles` fields that never existed on `DetectedArtifacts`.\n    30→\n    31→**Observations:**\n    32→- 16 test files had type errors vs 4 source files — tests were the primary debt vector.\n    33→\n    34→### 15-4-fix-ts-compilation-errors — code-review (2026-03-25T06:25Z)\n  